reviewText: I thoroughly enjoyed this video.  The techniques were illustrated well and I am more informed because of it.  I would highly recommend this video!

It's ok just two main styles the ones on the cover I really wanted to see more razor cutting techniques and slower and from different angles. In future produce a much more amateur friendly video showing cuts in 3 - 4 varying lengths or styles and please, please slow down and show the cuts at different angles.
